        <Parent_String>card games (activities) [300222738], games [300069657], public and interactive activities [300379951], physical activities by specific context [300239444], physical activities [300222722], Physical and Mental Activities (hierarchy name) [300222468], Activities Facet [300264090]</Parent_String>
